## Decisions

- [14:35] Rate limit: 100 requests per 60 seconds per API key. Rationale: matches Shopify's own rate limits, keeps us in sync with upstream.
- [15:10] Use `slowapi` library instead of custom middleware. Rationale: already handles Redis backend, sliding windows, and proper 429 responses. Less code to maintain.
